EmailTemplate.subject: We're excited to see you Wednesday!
EmailTemplate.textOnly: See you Wednesday! Blues Peer Insights 2022 November 2-3 | Orlando, FL We’re excited to see you Wednesday at our exclusive Blues event. Just a friendly reminder that the dress code for the event is business casual, so feel free to dress comfortably. You can also access our short pre-event survey <[[https://now.teladochealth.com/MTM4LURSSC03MDcAAAGHj6p90UlFzrxt4dLM5YpPBk_Ikb1BVWR9ve4p5Ymb4j0S9VvxCbRMn-McYSSTJbu9YcsANtM=]]> here. After checking in at the hotel, we will meet at the GuideWell Innovation Center for event check-in at 2:30 p.m. ET, Wednesday, November 2. See you soon! Visit the event page <[[https://now.teladochealth.com/MTM4LURSSC03MDcAAAGHj6p90aXUr5kpKxcyz1SMfoyP6k1TtjhDsvTjPeBaZbEsSBe1wgGFNiVSg0-rxjII99Ja03M=]]> to see our most recent agenda.
